# {{name}}

A game built on [Plinth](https://github.com/Luminary-Analytics/plinth) — the
stable base your game stands on.

## Run

```sh
cargo run
```

WASD to move, mouse to orbit the camera, space to jump.

## Edit

- Gameplay code lives in `src/` (Rust). The full Bevy ECS is available as a
  documented escape hatch.
- Levels and content live in `scenes/*.scene.json`. Edit them **while the
  game runs** — valid saves hot-reload in place, invalid saves log exactly
  what's wrong and leave the game running.
- Validate content without compiling anything: `plinth validate`.

The scene schema (great context for your coding agent) is published at
<https://github.com/Luminary-Analytics/plinth/blob/main/schemas/scene.schema.json>.
